   <body>
      <p>Participants are an additional set of customers or members which can be added to a program. For example, they can be members of IDN, members of GPO or set of independent customers. Adding the participants to this section make these set of customers/members eligible to a price defined in the program.</p>
      <p>Order lines can be uploaded for each of the participants and based on Benefit Level setting on the program header, the system shall calculate the aggregations for individual participants.</p>
      <p>This section also enables you to add, modify, import, export, and delete one or more participants in the program. For adding, modifying, and deleting the participants, please refer to the <xref href="../participants_102432701_102432701/102432701.xml" format="dita">Participants</xref> section.</p>
